    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior has some noticeable scratches and a few small dings, and the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it will eventually need a suspension tune-up and has a slow oil leak that requires monitoring. It\u2019s a solid, functional car that is priced to reflect its current state and upcoming maintenance needs.",
